            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chorizo is beginning to crisp, add your <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>tomatoes </strong>and <strong>soft cheese</strong> to the pan and give everything a good mix up</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
